-- China to Produce 50 Bcm of Tight Gas by 2015, Researcher Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2013-07-16T07:22:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-16/china-to-produce-50-bcm-of-tight-gas-by-2015-researcher-says.html
China  to see “production growth
peak” of tight gas during 2016 and 2020,  Sinopec (386)  says in
newsletter posted on website.
* Sinopec cites Zhang Donghui, researcher with Chinese Academy
of Social Sciences
* Tight-gas output to reach 80 bcm by 2020 and 100 bcm by 2030:
researcher
* China’s domestic gas output to reach 230 bcm by 2020;
unconventional gas to make up 52% of supply: researcher
* China’s shale gas and coal-bed methane output to reach 60 bcm
and 70 bcm, respectively, by 2030: researcher
*China to import 150 bcm of gas by 2020: researcher
*China to import 250 bcm of gas by 2030, with domestic output
estimated at 380 bcm: researcher  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
Sarah Chen in Beijing at 
